Interface Summary
IBaseCharacter The BaseCharacter-interface contains methods that must be implemented by any Character-object, for calculating and retrieving certain properties.

Health The Health-class representing a healthpool, acts as a data type, and contains properties for current and maximum health.

Monster The Monster-class represents a monster that the player can fight.
Player The Player class is used to represent a human player.
